{"id":261595,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/11/bbc-中国报摘：中美领导双双换届/","date":"2012-11-07T07:45:06Z","modified":"2012-11-07T07:45:06Z","title":"BBC | 中国报摘：中美领导双双换届","content":"<div>\n<div><img width=\"304\" height=\"171\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2012/11/07/121107051854_cn_beijing_us_election_304x171_reuters.jpg\" alt=\"一名中国客人在美国驻北京大使馆主办的大选派对上与奥巴马和罗姆尼的纸板人像合照（7/11/2012）\" /></p>\n<p>报道称许多中国网民透过社交媒体紧贴美国选情。</p>\n</div>\n<p>中美两国领导换班的消息是星期三（11月7日）中国报章同时关注的两大焦点。不少报章同时详尽报道中共十八大与美国总统选举。</p>\n<p>英文 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinadaily.com.cn%2Fcndy%2F2012-11%2F07%2Fcontent_15884586.htm\"><span>按键</span> <span>《中国日报》</span></a>与 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bjnews.com.cn%2Ffeature%2F2012%2F11%2F07%2F232031.html\"><span>按键</span> <span>《新京报》</span></a>等报道，中国全国各地的十八大代表团均已抵达北京，其中还包括26名农民工代表。报道称这体现了中国“基层民主”扩充。</p>\n<p>广州 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fgcontent.oeeee.com%2F8%2F9f%2F89f03f7d02720160%2FBlog%2F99a%2Fcf4963.html\"><span>按键</span> <span>《南方都市报》</span></a>与成都 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wccdaily.com.cn%2Fshtml%2Fhxdsb%2F20121107%2F39181.shtml\"><span>按键</span> <span>《华西都市报》</span></a>等转发了新华社的一篇述评。中共十八大将将部署“深水区”改革，但没有说明具体的改革内容。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.globaltimes.cn%2Fcontent%2F742801.shtml\"><span>按键</span> <span>《环球时报》英文版</span></a>发表该报民调称，中国大多数民众都相信，国家应当稳步开展政治改革。</p>\n<p>与此同时， <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.globaltimes.cn%2Fcontent%2F742799.shtml\"><span>按键</span> <span>《环球时报》英文版</span></a>等报章以美国总统选举作为头版头条， <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bjnews.com.cn%2Fworld%2F2012%2F11%2F07%2F232099.html\"><span>按键</span> <span>《新京报》</span></a>等地方报章也用上大篇幅报道选战。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fopinion.huanqiu.com%2Feditorial%2F2012-11%2F3251085.html\"><span>按键</span> <span>《环球时报》的双语社评</span></a>把美国选举与中国政治制度作比较。</p>\n<p>社评说：“选举制度鼓励了民粹主义，政党和政治家们都逐渐成为民粹主义的俘虏。”</p>\n<p>“从民权的字面意义来看，发生这一切就是对的。因为把民权发展到极端，就是要让每个人都尽可能实现利益大化。”</p>\n<p>“付出和吃苦变得很不合时宜，国家整体进步被置于相当次要的位置。”</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fhaiwai.people.com.cn%2Fn%2F2012%2F1107%2Fc232601-17684104.html\"><span>按键</span> <span>《人民日报海外版》的头版评论</span></a>也重申了中国领导人一向强调的，要发展“有中国特色”的民主之路。</p>\n<p>文章说：“我们的民主新路，要和平、稳定的民主政治，不要暴力连连、社会动荡；要统一、和谐的民主发展，不要国家分裂、一盘散沙；要繁荣发展的民主建设，不要经济停滞、生活倒退。”</p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://docs.google.com/a/chinadigitaltimes.net/spreadsheet/embeddedform?hl=zh-CN&#038;formkey=dGlaNkplWEluYV9TWUxDQkhfaDlxQmc6MQ\" width=\"510\" height=\"334\" frameborder=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\">Loading&#8230;</iframe></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代 </a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":998,"categories":[18270,18269,8779],"tags":[11945,19189]}